      "settings": {
        "section_preload": "true",
        "checksum": "3fe21fcfab8e5f77e7ccbffe8a8a7e5049e3674d62968ad238b2f5b81191f002_1_1_1_0__1",
        "ggviiph8ERl_text": "<p>AntiAge Night Cream • 50ml</p>",
        "ggSzrYgvgcA_text": "<p><strong>4.6 Excellent</strong> | 3,439+ reviews</p>",
        "ggVLmbUDTCI_text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:23px;\">\"I've been using it for 2 months... nobody believes my real age anymore!\"</span></p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_0": "<p>100% Made In Italy</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_1": "<p>Dermatologically Tested</p>",
        "gg81WwevIKk_childItem_2": "<p>Firms and smooths skin texture</p>",
        "ggXpA2NOkMM_text": "New: <strong>Omnis</strong> has become <strong>SerlinoLab</strong>.<br>Same formula, new look",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_label": "Add to Cart",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_outOfStockLabel": "Out of stock",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_unavailableLabel": "Unavailable",
        "ggbsEHDd1cH_variantSelectionRequiredMessage": "Please select a variant to add product to cart",
        "ggd3njxJyN7_text": "60-day Guarantee",
        "ggCdVdus-lO_text": "<p>If the product doesn't meet your expectations, you have up to 60 days to request a complete refund, without any complications.</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_0": "<p>What happened to Omnis? Why is it now SerlinoLab?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_1": "<p>Will SerlinoLab work for me?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_2": "<p>Can it be found in stores/pharmacies?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_3": "<p>How long does it last?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_4": "<p>How to use it?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_5": "<p>How long does it take to see results?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_6": "<p>How long does shipping take?</p>",
        "ggB9Gp8U8JQ_childItem_7": "<p>Where is the formula produced?</p>",
        "ggKRG7l40ZB_text": "<p>We updated our name and packaging to better reflect the true Italian identity of our brand.</p><p> </p><p>The formulas? Exactly the same.</p><p> </p><p>Same ingredients, same quality, same lab on the Amalfi Coast.</p><p>Just a new look.</p><p> </p><p>We hope you like it as much as we do</p>",
        "ggKZrkCgfQz_text": "<p><strong>Here's the honest truth: SerlinoLab works for the vast majority of men, but we can't promise it works for absolutely everyone.</strong></p><p> </p><p>Our formula has delivered results for thousands of Italian men aged 40+. The clinical studies prove it - 87% see significant wrinkle reduction in 8 weeks. But every man's skin is different, and we'd be lying if we said it's 100% guaranteed for everyone.</p><p> </p><p><strong>That's exactly why we offer the 60-day money-back guarantee.</strong> We don't want your money if SerlinoLab doesn't give you the younger, firmer skin you're looking for. Try it for two full months - if you don't see dramatic improvements, we'll refund every penny.</p>",
        "ggLuQ0nuQN8_text": "<p><strong>NO</strong> at the moment<strong> the SerlinoLab cream is only available on our website.</strong></p><p> </p><p>We just launched in the US and we have a very limited batch available.</p>",
        "ggR8kqovO2L_text": "<p><strong>1 bottle lasts exactly 1 month with daily use - which is why we recommend at least 2.</strong></p><p> </p><p><strong>Month 1</strong> gives initial improvements, but <strong>month 2</strong> is when 93% of men see dramatic results. Most men desperately search for more after seeing early changes.</p><p> </p><p>Plus our <strong>60-day money-back </strong>guarantee covers your entire transformation journey.</p>",
        "ggFipoBsWwP_text": "<p><strong>In the evening, </strong>after cleaning and drying your face, apply 1-2 doses on the clean face and massage with circular movements until completely absorbed. Bring the excess along the neck.</p>",
        "ggNgskm7d42_text": "<p><strong>Men notice improvements from the very first use, but the real transformation happens week by week.</strong></p><p> </p><p><strong>Week 1-2:</strong> skin feels immediately smoother and more hydrated. People start saying \"you look rested today.\"</p><p> </p><p><strong>Week 6-8:</strong> This is where the magic happens. 93% of men see a significant reduction in wrinkles and fine lines. Skin looks visibly younger, and people start asking \"what's your secret?\"</p><p> </p><p><strong>The science behind it:</strong> SerlinoLab works deep beneath the surface to stimulate collagen production - that's why it takes 6-8 weeks for the dramatic results. Unlike basic moisturizers that just sit on top, omnis uses a <strong>bio-identical form of Vitamin A</strong> your skin naturally stores. Your body recognizes it. It welcomes it in. So you get the collagen rebuilding of a prescription cream, with the gentleness of a moisturizer. All gain. No burn.</p><p> </p><p><strong>Here's the best part:</strong> <strong>60 days</strong> to see these results risk-free. If you don't look in the mirror after 8 weeks and see noticeably younger, firmer skin, we'll refund every penny. Thousands of men across Italy are already experiencing this transformation - <strong>try it yourself with zero risk</strong>.</p>",
        "ggg59nFYXJE_text": "<p>We ship from our <strong>warehouse in New Jersey</strong> within 24h of receiving your order!<br><br>You will receive your order in <strong>2-5 business days!</strong></p>",
        "ggWWrnyOmWZ_text": "<p>SerlinoLab is 100% formulated and made in italy 🇮🇹 following the strictest italian tests and regulation.</p><p> </p><p>Formulated with 95% natural ingredients, it contains:</p><p>NO Alcohol, No Paraben, No harsh silicones</p><p> </p><p>It's vegan, cruelty free. and dermatologically tested</p>"
      }
    },
